\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {72}{\ignorespaces Historical, parametric, and MC VaR estimates on the same Student-\(t_3\) loss sample: parametric-Normal systematically under-reports the tail. The diagnostic any FRTB-IMA bank runs daily --- and a corner of the analytical failure that left LTCM's daily VaR overrun by roughly \(40\times \) on the worst August-1998 day (and an order of magnitude more cumulatively)}}{500}{figure.0.72}\protected@file@percent }
